  line:
  - _profile: {fileID: -1996703693659354134, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Zoe
    _sentences: "We\u2019ve got enough of a littering problem without your slimes,
      don\u2019t we?"
  - _profile: {fileID: 3292930165984601596, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Khris
    _sentences: 'Woah, a real hero! Hi, I''m Khris.

      Aren''t my slimes super
      cute?'
  - _profile: {fileID: -1996703693659354134, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Zoe
    _sentences: "They\u2019re a bit too rabid for me.\r\nHand over whatever you made
      them with, dude."
  - _profile: {fileID: 3292930165984601596, guid: f0120b5629f3f4449a7fe99b64f1ab92,
      type: 3}
    _cutscene: {fileID: 0}
    _name: Khris
    _sentences: "Sorry but I'm not giving up yet.\r\nI\u2019ll prove I can handle
      this in a fun and fair battle. Ready? Go!"
